  "texts": [
    "We uniformly sampled approximately 1.1 million conversations, and then sampled one message within each conversation, with the following restrictions:",
    "We only include messages from May 2024 to July 2025.",
    "We exclude conversations from users who opted out of sharing their messages for model training.",
    "We exclude users who self-report their age as under 18.",
    "We exclude conversations that users have deleted and from users whose accounts have been deactivated or banned."
  ],
